# NAME
#	job_submit_all_partitions - determines if the JobSubmitPlugins includes "all_partitions"
#
# SYNOPSIS
#	job_submit_all_partitions
#
# DESCRIPTION
#	Use scontrol to determine if the JobSubmitPlugins
#	includes "all_partitions".
#
